ls.co.uk/news-press/latest-news/new-canon-pastor-appointed-at-st-pauls |title=New Canon Pastor appointed at St Paul's |publisher=St Paul's Cathedral |accessdate=18 February 2016}}\n* {{citation |last=Clark |first=John |year=1996 |chapter=The Temple of Diana |editor-last=Bird |editor-first=Joanna |editor2-last=Hassall |editor2-first=Mark |editor3-last=Sheldon |editor3-first=Harvey |display-editors=1 |title=Interpreting Roman London |publisher=Oxbow |series=Oxbow Monograph |volume=58 |location=Oxford |pages=1\u20139}}\n* {{citation |last=Denison |first=Simon |date=June 1995 |title=News: In Brief |work=British Archaeology |publisher=Council for British Archaeology |url=http://www.archaeologyuk.org/ba/ba5/BA5NEWS.HTML |accessdate=30 March 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513125933/http://www.archaeologyuk.org/ba/ba5/BA5NEWS.HTML |archivedate=13 May 2013}}\n* {{citation |last=Downes |first=Kerry |authorlink=Kerry Downes |year=1987 |title=Sir Christopher Wren: the Design of St Paul's Cathedral |location=London |publisher=Trefoil Publications |pages=11\u201334}}\n* {{citation |last=Dunton |first=Larkin |year=1896 |title=The World and Its People |publisher=Silver, Burdett |pages=25\u201326}}\n* {{citation |author=EI staff |date=19 April 1941 |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=950&dat=19410419&id=xgJQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DVUDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2535,715297 |title=St. Paul's Cathedral in London Hit by Bomb |newspaper=[[The Evening Independent]]}}\n* {{citation |last=Fletcher |first=Banister |authorlink=Banister Fletcher |year=1962 |title=A History of Architecture on the Comparative Method (seventeenth edition) |publisher=Athlone Press, University of London}}<!---NOTE: Do not change this to the 2001 edition. The writer of this does not own a new edition. The page references are to the seventeenth edition (1962).--->\n* {{citation |last=Geffen |first=Anthony (producer) |date=8 July 2014 |chapter=Time Scanners: St. Paul's Cathedral |title=Scanners |ch